# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
!*.tfvars.example
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# Keep provider lock files
!**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# Secrets / keys — never commit
*.pem
*.key
*-private-key*
.env

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/

# Local tooling state / scaffolding (ruflo / claude-flow) — never publish
.claude-flow/
.swarm/
ruvector.db
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
# Uncomment to also exclude the ruflo/claude workspace config from the repo:
# .claude/
# CLAUDE.md
